Text: Vafan...JAg fick nå jävla skit när jag registrerade mej med er serial o användarnamn om att dom hade skickat in nått till åklagaren och att jah kunde få böter på 250000 dollar

Yup, thats life...

Why use pirated software.... Have you tried to read the *.nfo file before using the program... It states clear that you should patch the program before using it, and as always... All programs you download and use are done on your behalf.... Don't blame the mailman, blame the sender...
